We value our long-standing relationships with our clients. As such, we are committed to working with our clients both during negotiations and after to facilitate their day-to-day relationships and operations. By leveraging our founder’s skills as a seasoned transactional attorney with her knowledge in the areas of technology and intellectual property, we are able to offer our clients unique service in the following areas:

